<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h3>A demonstration of how to access a SELECT element</h3>

<style>
body{
  background-color:black;
  color:white;
  font-family: Comic Sans MS,arial,helvetica,sans-serif, "微軟正黑體", "Microsoft JhengHei", "新細明體", "PMingLiU", "細明體", "MingLiU", "標楷體", "DFKai-sb", serif;
}
.item {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 200px;
  margin: 1em;
}
.words{ 
  font-size: 12px;
  color: white;
  top:10%;  
  left: 20%;
}
.box2 {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 200px;
  height: 100px;
  margin: 10em;
}
.display{
  margin: 20px auto;
